Other assets[edit]
Liberty Media is a prominent investor. In addition to its own offerings, the company also owns the stock of several major media and telecommunication companies. As of December 22, 2013,[46] Liberty has a stake in the following companies not listed above:


Associated Partners, L.P. (37%)
Barnes & Noble, Inc. (2%)
CenturyLink, Inc. (1%)
Charter Communications Inc. (27%)
Crown Media Holdings Inc. (3%)
Ideiasnet (27%)
Kroenke Arena Company, LLC (7%)
Live Nation Entertainment Inc. (26%)
Mobile Streams Plc (16%)
Sirius XM Radio, Inc. (53%)
Sprint Corporation (1%)
Time Warner Cable, Inc. (1%)
Time Warner, Inc. (1%)
Viacom Inc. (1%)


